OL,3,CMum heard 'last gurgling breaths' of
OL,4,Ccar-loving son as life support turned
OL,5,Coff
OL,7,FThe car went over a ravine and landed
OL,8,Fon its roof onto a wall, with Justin's
OL,9,Fhead hitting it.
OL,11,FDr Alger recalls the knock at the door
OL,12,Ffrom one of Justin's friends, who,
OL,13,Fwhite faced, told her there had been
OL,14,Fan accident.
OL,16,F"We had a knock on the door at around
OL,17,Fmidnight, it sounds strange but I knew
OL,18,Fsomething bad had happened, part of me
OL,19,Fknew that my son had died."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
