OL,4,Ccar-loving son as life support turned
OL,5,Coff
OL,7,FShe rushed to the scene along the A6
OL,8,Fnear Dove Holes in the High Peak, a
OL,9,Fnotoriously bendy stretch of road.
OL,11,FJustin was on a stretcher and gasping
OL,12,Ffor his last breaths. He was taken to
OL,13,Fhospital where it was found he had a
OL,14,Fcatastrophic brain injury which he
OL,15,Fwould not survive.
OL,17,FAfter taking him off life support, his
OL,18,Ffamily stayed with him over the next
OL,19,Ftwo hours.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
