OL,3,CMum heard 'last gurgling breaths' of
OL,4,Ccar-loving son as life support turned
OL,5,Coff
OL,7,F"That was the moment that our lives
OL,8,Freally changed for good. I couldn't
OL,9,Fcook, I couldn't dress myself and to
OL,10,Fbe honest, I just wanted to die. That
OL,11,Flasted for two years, and I got to the
OL,12,Fpoint where I really started to beat
OL,13,Fmyself up.
OL,15,F"I have another child to look after,
OL,16,Fbut you cut yourself off emotionally
OL,17,Ffrom everybody. I cut myself off from
OL,18,Fmy son, from my husband; I spent the
OL,19,Frest of my waking hours thinking about
OL,20,Fwhat the best way to join Justin would
OL,21,Fbe."
