OL,7,FSteph is now using her grief to
OL,8,Feducate others about the need to drive
OL,9,Fcarefully and consider the conditions
OL,10,Fof the road, working with Derbyshire
OL,11,FPolice.
OL,13,FShe says that speed limits are there
OL,14,Ffor a reason, they're not a target
OL,15,Fspeed to maintain at every corner.
OL,17,F"I don't like to describe him as a boy
OL,18,Fracer as it makes him sound less of a
OL,19,Fvictim, but he liked his car.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
