OL,5,Coff
OL,7,F"Speeding is not worth it; you've got
OL,8,Fdreams and you've got aspirations."
OL,10,FJustin was a media student at Buxton
OL,11,FCollege with aspirations of studying
OL,12,Flaw at university.
OL,14,F"Justin has lost his aspirations, his
OL,15,Fdreams, he's lost the opportunity to
OL,16,Fhave children and a wife, a good job."
