OL,7,FPolice Constable Cork, a member of
OL,8,FDerbyshire Police's Roads Policing
OL,9,FUnit, says: "The vast majority of the
OL,10,Fpeople I speak to on a daily basis
OL,11,Faren't your typical 'criminals' that
OL,12,Fwe would normally deal with.
