OL,4,Ccar-loving son as life support turned
OL,5,Coff
OL,7,F"We don't often deal with shoplifters
OL,8,For career criminals, in our job we are
OL,9,Foften dealing with people who have
OL,10,Fnever been in trouble with the police,
OL,11,Fwho maybe have never once dealt with
OL,12,Fpolice before. Somebody could be on
OL,13,Fthe way to the airport - or returning
OL,14,Ffrom it - and have been involved in a
OL,15,Fcollision and they have lost their
OL,16,Flife as a result.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
