OL,5,Coff
OL,7,F"Nobody on the morning of a collision
OL,8,Fleft the house thinking, 'I'll never
OL,9,Fcome back'. That is difficult to deal
OL,10,Fwith from our side of things, from my
OL,11,Fown experience it's awful to deal
OL,12,Fwith, but I cannot imagine the untold
OL,13,Fmisery that it causes for families and
OL,14,Ffriends of those involved."
